Package: distrcox
Type: Package
Title: Package for simulating Cox proportional hazards distributions
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-01-12
Author: Nicola Dinapoli
Maintainer: Nicola Dinapoli <nicola.dinapoli@rm.unicatt.it>
Description: This package allows to simulate Cox proportional hazards
    distributions by creating de-novo case series or by using baseline hazards
    achieved by other Cox models fitted by using coxph function
License: GPL-2
Depends:
    survival, muhaz
Imports:
    survival (>= 2.37-7), muhaz (>= 1.2.6)
LazyData: true
